{"tid":1422940,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"開返個前線訓練班好冇？","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T14:44:47.000Z","uid":47170,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6c594e3f3b14a11b7951ff9a0dee944a67de9f76","tid":1422940,"uid":47170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:25:30.000Z","msg":"睇live見到唔少和理非想入行做勇武<br />\n但又唔識點樣做<br />\n最多都係換套gear企上前線<br />\n但一遇到危機嘅時候 就走都走唔切<br />\n勇武嘅好易會覺得和理非要人幫手救<br />\n而和理非又覺得自己已經盡做幫拖 點解要鬧<br />\n<br />\n其實前線好易愈拉愈少人<br />\n增加前線人數係必須的<br />\n所以如果有心嘅和理非想出去幫拖<br />\n不如搵返個勇武帶路<br />\n好似啲母雞帶雞仔咁<br />\n<br />\n一開始可能係教班雞仔前線心態<br />\n有咩係一定要知 有咩唔可以做咁<br />\n再逐步逐步帶佢哋做個supporter<br />\n之後再發展其他技能<br />\n<br />\n我都係9up下<br />\n<br />\n不如大家一齊構思下"},{"pid":"47cfb67f1901131a53890540e3431270cf31e86d","tid":1422940,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:35:55.000Z","msg":"（突發）（多圖） 炮台山勁多狗同狗車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"390dc654678dfc68135558e0a07d64e8566ad4d5","tid":1422940,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"逄星期六？仔仔朝早要返學"},{"pid":"b62fc9003f0cf79095436e7b9c13bdae5f6c7804","tid":1422940,"uid":230882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:37:31.000Z","msg":"好易俾狗一野捉晒"},{"pid":"ce4018ab071b938306bc42729a426ca67d067c34","tid":1422940,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:39:29.000Z","msg":"要有死同殺人勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />琴晚果班真係有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n火槍用幾次係人都識用啦"},{"pid":"a81c2fc4d2d691c37462092362e9b8092a268fb8","tid":1422940,"uid":47170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"390dc654678dfc68135558e0a07d64e8566ad4d5","tid":1422940,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"逄星期六？仔仔朝早要返學"},"cited